e":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"2685632547","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2685632547","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjY4NTYzMjU0Nw==","status":"current","title":"Vulnerabilidades","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10593389},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2685632547/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2685632547/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2685632547/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2685632547/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2685632547","tinyui":"/x/I4ATo","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2685632547","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2685632547/Vulnerabilidades","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2685632547"}},{"id":"3638231064","type":"folder","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:folder/activation/3feb9026-40ef-4a53-9bfd-75d0dc16e0f6/3638231064","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmZvbGRlci9hY3RpdmF0aW9uLzNmZWI5MDI2LTQwZWYtNGE1My05YmZkLTc1ZDBkYzE2ZTBmNi8zNjM4MjMxMDY0","status":"current","title":"Michi Token","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":499144397},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3638231064/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3638231064/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3638231064/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3638231064/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3638231064","editui":"/spaces/BAN/folder/3638231064","webui":"/spaces/BAN/folder/3638231064","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/folder/3638231064"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"3b8782b9-de91-40eb-8c1b-d9c2a20edea6\"><ac:rich-text-body><p>Este documento representa el tasking y estimaci&oacute;n para Michi Token, a cargo de <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"6120132dc2f3a50069115a19\" ri:local-id=\"2fb07f5f-d044-4e8f-afbd-a425d27b934b\" /></ac:link> .</p><p>Las horas totales estimadas son de <strong>395</strong>.</p><p>Fecha de Inicio: <strong>Martes </strong><time datetime=\"2025-03-04\" /> </p><p>Fecha Estimada de Entrega: <strong>Lunes </strong><time datetime=\"2025-05-14\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 184.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 409.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 165.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>M&oacute;dulo</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>auth-service</p></td><td><p>Investigar c&oacute;mo podemos resolver la validaci&oacute;n de autenticaci&oacute;n de un usuario desde la API de Michi</p></td><td><p>4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar endpoint para autenticar usuario desde la API de Michi</p><p><strong>Comentarios:</strong></p><p><em>Esto est&aacute; sujeto a la tarea de arriba, en el caso de ya existir una forma de realizar esta autenticaci&oacute;n, esta tarea no aplica.</em></p></td><td><p>24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Agregar endpoint para bloquear un usuario por cierto tiempo.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>billing-service</p></td><td><p>Agregar columna en los productos para indicar si requiere validaci&oacute;n con Michi</p></td><td><p>4</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Modificar CRUD de productos para crear/modificar esa columna.</p></td><td><p>8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Crear tabla de dispositivos de confianza de los usuarios. Debe tener el token, platform y el user_id.</p></td><td><p> 8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar CRUD para los dispositivos de confianza de los usuarios.</p></td><td><p>24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Agregar endpoint para enviar push al dispositivo de confianza de un usuario. Para esto, vamos a tener que agregar un notification type nuevo que identifique a este tipo de notificaciones.</p></td><td><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Al endpoint de pago, agregarle la recepci&oacute;n de un OTP que vamos a tener que validar contra michi.</p></td><td><p>24</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>external-services</p></td><td><p>Agregar endpoint para validar OTP contra Michi.</p></td><td><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Agregar operaci&oacute;n para el request new otp de Michi.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>notification-service</p></td><td><p>Agregar endpoint para enviar push notification recibiendo el token, platform, data (incluye el tipo de notificaci&oacute;n) y message.</p></td><td><p>32</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>bportal</p></td><td><p>En el login, enviar push al dispositivo de confianza del usuario. Esto peg&aacute;ndole al endpoint de billing-service.</p><p>Comentario:</p><p>En el caso de que el usuario no tenga un dispositivo de confianza, no le permitiremos el login y le mostraremos un error.</p><p>En el caso de que tenga un dispositivo de confianza, el portal deber&aacute; triggerear el envio de la notificaci&oacute;n y abrir un socket para esperar el aviso por parte de la app.</p></td><td><p>32</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Crear un endpoint para recibir el callback por parte del servicio y hacer el broadcast al socket para continuar el login del usuario.</p></td><td><p>28</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Al intentar pagar un servicio que requiere validaci&oacute;n de pin, enviar push al dispositivo de confianza para iniciar la validaci&oacute;n. Luego de esto, abrir un socket para esperar el aviso por parte de la app.</p></td><td><p>32</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Crear Modal y vista para el doble factor de seguridad en login.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Agregar l&oacute;gica para bloqueo de usuario en el login.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Crear Modales para la confirmaci&oacute;n de pago con soft token.</p><p>Incluye modal de success, carga e intento fallido.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>Agregar l&oacute;gica para confirmaci&oacute;n de pago con soft token e intento fallido.</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#e3fcef\"><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p /></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>GENERAL</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>Revisiones y correcciones de PRS, deploys, pruebas de ambiente</p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#ffffff\"><p>24</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">344</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">51</p></td></tr><tr><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p /></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>395</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3639345154"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":584},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3639345154/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3639345154/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3639345154/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3639345154/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3639345154","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3639345154/Michi+Token+-+Tasking+y+Estimaci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3639345154","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3639345154","tinyui":"/x/AgDs2","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}